main: ^As you may have been able to tell from my adorably small top hat and mustache, I am indeed the mayor of this town.
^I've heard quite a bit about you and your interest in me.
^I assure you, whatever you think you may or may not have seen in the cave outside town doesn't exist.
^There are no monsters in Fish City!
^No matter what you say, no matter what anyone says.
^Now, I think it's quite time you left our city. Don't come back.
